# Title: Impacket PsExec Execution
# Author: Bhabesh Raj
# Date: 2020-12-14
# Level: high
# Description: Detects execution of Impacket's psexec.py.
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, attack.t1021.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_impacket_psexec.yml

EventID=5145 RelativeTargetName IN ("*RemCom_stdin*", "*RemCom_stdout*", "*RemCom_stderr*") ShareName="\\\\\*\\IPC$"